{"_id":"MhGzcPyPlksP4Wzo","name":"Tier 4 Melee Critical Hits (Levels 13-20)","description":"Critical hit effects for melee attacks at Tier 4 (Levels 13-20). Legendary effects for legendary adventurers.","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-sword-slashing-red.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"Qi2UlFfZOUpF1Eqp","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your critical strike deals damage as normal, but no additional effect occurs.","img":"icons/svg/d20-highlight.svg","weight":6,"range":[1,6],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"J1CdewsBldfTbheg","type":0,"text":"Crippled Arm - Your strike ruins the target's weapon arm. They take -2 to attack rolls until healed with Regenerate or similar magic.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[7,14],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"k67daSZP20T9jPHw","type":0,"text":"Pain Overload - Blinding waves of pain wrack the target. They have disadvantage on all attacks until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":8,"range":[15,22],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Pain Overload","duration":1}}},{"_id":"LYvKydIilaGypwlw","type":0,"text":"Rattled - The thunderous impact scatters the target's wits. They have disadvantage on their ability checks until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":7,"range":[23,29],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"ability.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Rattled","duration":1}}},{"_id":"tDZ7iSvagXsLoFsT","type":0,"text":"Disoriented - Your blow leaves the target's senses swimming. They have disadvantage on all saving throws until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":7,"range":[30,36],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Disoriented","duration":1}}},{"_id":"JAONePzf4YNt7BHi","type":0,"text":"Armor Shattered - Your devastating strike caves in the target's armor. They take -3 AC until it is repaired with smith's tools or magic.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":6,"range":[37,42],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-3,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"Cz7PqN9Rjkh2sZw4","type":0,"text":"Sundered Plate - Your blow rips a section of armor away entirely. The target takes -4 AC until it is repaired by a master smith.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":6,"range":[43,48],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-4,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"tIqpeRUKAkFP3x26","type":0,"text":"Driving Slam - You drive your full weight into the blow. The target must succeed on a DC 17 Strength save or be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":6,"range":[49,54],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"str","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"6kuXB4wxn0t84nWA","type":0,"text":"Mortal Wound - Your strike opens a mortal wound. The target takes three extra weapon dice of damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":5,"range":[55,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"FZvGX1x5PQSu7Yym","type":0,"text":"Blood in the Eyes - A gout of blood blinds the target. They are blinded until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"KcJ0A9w5DnL6BZsO","type":0,"text":"Gut Wound - Your blade rips through the target's innards. They must succeed on a DC 17 Constitution save or be poisoned until they receive healing.","img":"icons/svg/poison.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"poisoned","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"MI9PeBeup5JajdaG","type":0,"text":"Pinning Strike - Your weapon hooks the target and pins them in place. They are grappled until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"grappled","duration":1}}},{"_id":"4o3lk2Xj9ndlUbFH","type":0,"text":"Hamstrung - Your blade severs the tendons of the target's leg. They are restrained until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":5,"range":[75,79],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"restrained","duration":1}}},{"_id":"35C86pNNLZaJlwC3","type":0,"text":"Completely Exposed - Your strike leaves the target utterly open. Attacks against them have advantage for 3 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":4,"range":[80,83],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Completely Exposed","duration":3}}},{"_id":"0Ox7nzIoWB2JrB6T","type":0,"text":"Terror Incarnate - Your devastating strike fills the target with dread. They must succeed on a DC 17 Wisdom save or be frightened of you for 3 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":4,"range":[84,87],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"wis","effectCondition":"frightened","duration":3}}},{"_id":"xLGgye5Xi1EMfm0K","type":0,"text":"Disemboweling Strike - Your blade guts the target. They must succeed on a DC 17 Constitution save or be incapacitated until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[88,91],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"incapacitated","duration":1}}},{"_id":"LuZG3FPtXI32etSY","type":0,"text":"Overwhelming Power - Your devastating blow lands with crushing force. The target takes four extra weapon dice of damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":3,"range":[92,94],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"4W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"6vOxG6Wl1xnsNzvj","type":0,"text":"Crippling Wound - Your devastating blow maims a limb. The target has disadvantage on all attack rolls until healed with Regenerate or similar magic.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":3,"range":[95,97],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Crippled Limb","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"eyxxNEXAAmL8nSH3","type":0,"text":"Deep Organ Strike - Your blade pierces something vital. The target must succeed on a DC 17 Constitution save or be paralyzed until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":2,"range":[98,99],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"paralyzed","duration":1}}},{"_id":"Ovs8EkzN2uUIIKbu","type":0,"text":"Devastating Strike - Your blow strikes with lethal precision. The target must succeed on a DC 17 Constitution save or take an extra 6d10 damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","damageFormula":"6d10","damageType":"weapon"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":4,"attackType":"melee","resultType":"crit"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783951849387,"modifiedTime":1783951849387,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"IWVc9H4t337Eu82A","name":"Tier 4 Melee Fumbles (Levels 13-20)","description":"Fumble effects for melee attacks at Tier 4 (Levels 13-20). Even legends can fail catastrophically.","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-sword-slashing-red.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"bLQS0kgvPOT1qCYM","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - You stumble but recover with no additional penalty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","weight":6,"range":[1,6],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"UcZUoyJc40FfqcKB","type":0,"text":"Jarred Wrist - You jar your wrist on the botched swing, taking a -2 penalty to attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[7,14],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"PCKxvyG34ivROkWx","type":0,"text":"Off Your Feet - You lurch off balance and have disadvantage on your next saving throw.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":8,"range":[15,22],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Off Your Feet","duration":0}}},{"_id":"9BV585zDuKBwWZi8","type":0,"text":"Lost Grip - Your weapon twists in your hand. You have disadvantage on your next melee weapon attack.","img":"icons/svg/sword.svg","weight":7,"range":[23,29],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.mwak","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Lost Grip","duration":0}}},{"_id":"IW3zNvNsmh09N5jY","type":0,"text":"Dropped Guard - You drop your guard, taking a -2 penalty to your AC until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":7,"range":[30,36],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"8jugllIhc20juaAn","type":0,"text":"Weapon Badly Damaged - Your weapon is badly damaged. You take a -3 penalty to attack rolls until it is repaired.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":6,"range":[37,42],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-3,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"ex1sOvpKFMXDVMEu","type":0,"text":"Shaken Confidence - Your failure rattles you to your core. You have disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":6,"range":[43,48],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Shaken Confidence","duration":1}}},{"_id":"iINmbcxk2SH8bpDM","type":0,"text":"Utterly Exposed - Your catastrophic failure leaves you completely vulnerable. Attacks against you have advantage for 3 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":6,"range":[49,54],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Utterly Exposed","duration":3}}},{"_id":"rz1ed8N4e4YdiCVr","type":0,"text":"Severe Self-Injury - You critically wound yourself. Take 3d6 damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":5,"range":[55,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3d6","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"D3eiNPx3Xq7To9C7","type":0,"text":"Sprawled - Your wild swing throws you off balance and you fall prone.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"9B04ICcdws3Zi563","type":0,"text":"Ears Ringing - Your own clumsy blow rings your helm like a bell. You are deafened until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"deafened","duration":1}}},{"_id":"CVQ7jd4yUVrbwAWu","type":0,"text":"Rattled - Your fumble rattles your nerve. You are frightened until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"frightened","duration":1}}},{"_id":"TA2esZuj44la1OlC","type":0,"text":"Weapon Flung - Your weapon flies from your grasp, landing well out of reach.","img":"icons/svg/sword.svg","weight":5,"range":[75,79],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disarm"}}},{"_id":"q2uHrkFTwdgpqdyT","type":0,"text":"Hit Yourself Critically - Your weapon rebounds and strikes you critically. Take 3d8 damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[80,83],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3d8","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"OoFDIybJlOieKObP","type":0,"text":"Concussed Yourself - You crack your own skull with the pommel. You are stunned until the start of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":4,"range":[84,87],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"stunned","duration":0}}},{"_id":"iy1Gifp6uFgDYxe8","type":0,"text":"Incapacitated - Your catastrophic failure leaves you reeling. You are incapacitated until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":4,"range":[88,91],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"incapacitated","duration":1}}},{"_id":"7HfNSV5dgilkqMeJ","type":0,"text":"Blown Wind - The reckless effort leaves you gasping. You gain one level of exhaustion.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":3,"range":[92,94],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"exhaustion","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"gFTgHQqT5IbzFB11","type":0,"text":"Devastating Self-Wound - Your weapon rebounds catastrophically. Take 4d8 damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":3,"range":[95,97],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"4d8","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"IRvRoSZi9ksN6HLt","type":0,"text":"Wild Swing - Your uncontrolled swing hits your nearest ally. Roll an attack against that ally's AC; on a hit, deal weapon damage.","img":"icons/svg/combat.svg","weight":2,"range":[98,99],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"attackAlly"}}},{"_id":"ctD3AO7KtEXFcMe0","type":0,"text":"Grievous Overswing - You overcommit with legendary force. Make a DC 17 Constitution saving throw or take 4d6 damage and fall prone.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"prone","damageFormula":"4d6","damageType":"weapon"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":4,"attackType":"melee","resultType":"fumble"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783951849387,"modifiedTime":1783951849387,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"p9ohRwMV9MVlouOi","name":"Tier 4 Ranged Critical Hits (Levels 13-20)","description":"Critical hit effects for ranged attacks at Tier 4 (Levels 13-20). Legendary effects for legendary adventurers.","img":"icons/weapons/bows/longbow-recurve-brown.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"uU9c5ne6VBWzNSQW","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your critical strike deals damage as normal, but no additional effect occurs.","img":"icons/svg/d20-highlight.svg","weight":6,"range":[1,6],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"zUi4ax0xMdU46fX6","type":0,"text":"Severed Tendon - Your shot severs a tendon in the target's arm, giving them -2 to attack rolls until they receive healing.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[7,14],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"l21i7oExJyVAB3yW","type":0,"text":"Suppressing Shot - A relentless hail of covering fire pins the target down, giving them disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":8,"range":[15,22],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Suppressed","duration":1}}},{"_id":"Z52JrcATkikNv8dm","type":0,"text":"Staggering Shot - Your shot staggers the target completely, giving them disadvantage on attacks and saving throws until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":7,"range":[23,29],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":["attack.all","save.all"],"effectName":"Staggered","duration":1}}},{"_id":"twEDrn1y6h5tFany","type":0,"text":"Armor Destroyed - Your shot ruins a section of the target's armor, imposing -4 AC until it is replaced or magically repaired.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":7,"range":[30,36],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-4,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"eJr8ACpdlmuOubN5","type":0,"text":"Crippling Devastation - Your shot shatters bone after bone, leaving the target with disadvantage on attacks until magically healed.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":6,"range":[37,42],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Crippled","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"IaU4JktEcwkig86P","type":0,"text":"Grit in the Eye - A spray of grit and blood catches the target across the eyes, leaving them blinded until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":6,"range":[43,48],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"Zs6mSFzBs2GaQzZ8","type":0,"text":"Completely Exposed - Your shot lays the target's defenses bare, granting advantage on attacks against them for three rounds.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":6,"range":[49,54],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Completely Exposed","duration":3}}},{"_id":"Pi8TXIruuJdlx3I5","type":0,"text":"Bleeder - The wound opens wide and bleeds freely, dealing an extra 2d6 piercing damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":5,"range":[55,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"piercing"}}},{"_id":"JJSKAuixCuJQRiBF","type":0,"text":"Devastating Impact - Your shot strikes with tremendous force, dealing an extra three weapon dice of damage.","img":"icons/svg/thrust.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"GNOh76uT6JrghB2t","type":0,"text":"Kneecapped - Your shot shatters the target's knee, forcing a DC 17 Dexterity save or be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"dex","effectCondition":"prone"}}},{"_id":"K2zfWK1KmVKkBpOV","type":0,"text":"Blinding Strike - Your shot ruins the target's eyes, blinding them until healed by Regenerate or similar magic.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"07LE4sFJbhigaZJ3","type":0,"text":"Nailed Down - The projectile nails the target to the ground, leaving them restrained until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":5,"range":[75,79],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"restrained","duration":1}}},{"_id":"olWdQ2dx2tgu8tiL","type":0,"text":"Deep Puncture - Your projectile buries itself deep, dealing an extra maximized weapon die of damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":4,"range":[80,83],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1WB","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"qdLFPJqjqzRCsPAv","type":0,"text":"Sinking Terror - A shot to a vital spot fills the target with dread, forcing a DC 17 Wisdom save or be frightened of you.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":4,"range":[84,87],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"wis","effectCondition":"frightened"}}},{"_id":"z8Crg6XKMu9VtqOJ","type":0,"text":"Overwhelming Shot - Your legendary shot tears through the target, dealing an extra four weapon dice of damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":4,"range":[88,91],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"4W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"0F81wtaX7Q2MPtAl","type":0,"text":"Punctured Lung - Your shot punctures a lung, forcing a DC 17 Constitution save or be poisoned while the target struggles to breathe.","img":"icons/svg/poison.svg","weight":3,"range":[92,94],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"poisoned"}}},{"_id":"tqQRHJzCuufk5vwn","type":0,"text":"Skull Ringer - The impact rattles the target's skull, forcing a DC 17 Constitution save or be stunned until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":3,"range":[95,97],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"stunned"}}},{"_id":"kmfvAOECLmxIqKBO","type":0,"text":"Crippling Volley - A crippling barrage overwhelms the target's body, inflicting one level of exhaustion until they recover.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":2,"range":[98,99],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"exhaustion","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"Qmx4rQhOyJwbi59D","type":0,"text":"Heart-Piercing Shot - Your shot seeks the heart, forcing a DC 17 Constitution save or take an extra 6d10 damage.","img":"icons/svg/skull.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","damageFormula":"6d10","damageType":"piercing"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":4,"attackType":"ranged","resultType":"crit"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783951849387,"modifiedTime":1783951849387,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"JRpTdQcGwXyyvQJZ","name":"Tier 4 Ranged Fumbles (Levels 13-20)","description":"Fumble effects for ranged attacks at Tier 4 (Levels 13-20). Even legends can fail catastrophically.","img":"icons/weapons/bows/longbow-recurve-brown.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"YKsJ7EDd8TrBkPt2","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your shot goes wide but you recover with no additional penalty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","weight":6,"range":[1,6],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"OJrgnPAkVuLH9ZjP","type":0,"text":"Watering Eyes - Your eyes water from the effort and you have disadvantage on your next ability check.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[7,14],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"ability.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Watering Eyes","duration":0}}},{"_id":"6mlxZf5kfAxSMUYp","type":0,"text":"Flinch - You flinch at your own misfire and have disadvantage on your next saving throw.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[15,22],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Flinch","duration":0}}},{"_id":"xQOVczfzzP8cr9tb","type":0,"text":"Snapped String - Your bowstring snaps taut awkwardly and you have disadvantage on ranged attacks until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":7,"range":[23,29],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.rwak","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Snapped String","duration":1}}},{"_id":"dFZVdXhrVHMSJaCc","type":0,"text":"Fouled Aim - Your aim is thrown off and you have disadvantage on your next attack roll.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":7,"range":[30,36],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Fouled Aim","duration":0}}},{"_id":"IJ6nmWYgzTNFEQPI","type":0,"text":"Overdrawn - You overdraw and wrench your form, taking a -2 penalty to attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":6,"range":[37,42],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"2Q1hirvkWWufvTsD","type":0,"text":"Recoil Strain - The recoil wrenches your arm; take 1d8 bludgeoning damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":6,"range":[43,48],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d8","damageType":"bludgeoning"}}},{"_id":"ZGfXDKMsyZKEugCe","type":0,"text":"Telegraphed Shot - You telegraph your shot and your target has advantage on its next saving throw against you.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":6,"range":[49,54],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Telegraphed Shot","duration":0}}},{"_id":"de8OdF3W4Ojf72d3","type":0,"text":"Caught Flat - You are caught flat-footed; attacks against you have advantage until the start of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":5,"range":[55,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Caught Flat","duration":1}}},{"_id":"vpzWxC4cxLgZltHP","type":0,"text":"Jammed Solid - Your weapon jams solid and you have disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Jammed Solid","duration":1}}},{"_id":"lGB2khARnJVwuOrC","type":0,"text":"Exposed Flank - Your stance collapses, leaving a -3 penalty to your AC until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-3,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"8A1G1syDsqhJXu9y","type":0,"text":"Dropped Weapon - Your ranged weapon flies from your hands, landing 30 feet away.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disarm"}}},{"_id":"DI7dwJllEQ3agaoS","type":0,"text":"Off-Balance - You lose your footing; make a DC 17 Dexterity saving throw or fall prone.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[75,79],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"dex","effectCondition":"prone","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"HTLmhnROq9LiG4So","type":0,"text":"Winded - The strain wracks your body; make a DC 17 Constitution saving throw or take 2d8 bludgeoning damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[80,83],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","damageFormula":"2d8","damageType":"bludgeoning"}}},{"_id":"7LCNxDo76wT7f85W","type":0,"text":"Stinging Rebound - Your shot rebounds savagely into you; take 3d8 damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[84,87],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3d8","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"PuA2bk4SATgpUskk","type":0,"text":"Blinded - A backlash of string and splinters blinds you until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":4,"range":[88,91],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":1}}},{"_id":"K2T3vW1NL3m4OA5g","type":0,"text":"Incapacitated - Your fumble leaves you reeling; you are incapacitated until the start of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":3,"range":[92,94],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"incapacitated","duration":1}}},{"_id":"IhvaqpKj407QAq2K","type":0,"text":"Devastating Rebound - Your projectile rebounds catastrophically into you; take 4d8 damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":3,"range":[95,97],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"4d8","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"SWr2BtCoH0bLELMW","type":0,"text":"Pulled Muscle - You tear something deep inside; you gain one level of exhaustion until you recover.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":2,"range":[98,99],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"exhaustion","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"wSLSfvtok7ZcphbW","type":0,"text":"Wild Ricochet - Your shot ricochets wildly toward the nearest ally; roll an attack against their AC.","img":"icons/svg/combat.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"attackAlly"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":4,"attackType":"ranged","resultType":"fumble"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783951849387,"modifiedTime":1783951849387,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"xaOGlwjpDwVfDBw7","name":"Tier 4 Spell Critical Hits (Levels 13-20)","description":"Critical hit effects for spell attacks at Tier 4 (Levels 13-20). Legendary effects for legendary adventurers.","img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-fireball-smoke-strong-orange.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"fkt0vNgGotIsncKG","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your critical spell deals damage as normal, but no additional effect occurs.","img":"icons/svg/d20-highlight.svg","weight":6,"range":[1,6],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"48h3cNx7uwEtP7VP","type":0,"text":"Sluggish Mind - The target's thoughts turn to sludge, giving them disadvantage on saving throws until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":8,"range":[7,14],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Sluggish Mind","duration":1}}},{"_id":"HPx07BxlkUuaWGkd","type":0,"text":"Hex of Frailty - A hex of frailty erodes the target's defenses, giving them a -2 penalty to AC until removed.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[15,22],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"bh0X6BOwMZ9BvTbW","type":0,"text":"Searing Flash - A blinding burst of arcane light sears the target's eyes, leaving them blinded until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":7,"range":[23,29],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"IWsJLDbGQSCHaLg3","type":0,"text":"Magic Disruption - Your spell disrupts the target's magic. They have disadvantage on spell attacks and saves for 3 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/silenced.svg","weight":7,"range":[30,36],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":["attack.msak","attack.rsak","save.all"],"effectName":"Magic Disruption","duration":3}}},{"_id":"L8rtqPAOCP8B7LON","type":0,"text":"Mana Burn - Raw magic ignites the target's own reserves, dealing 2d6 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":6,"range":[37,42],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"bbjQsMIZxilsFsXF","type":0,"text":"Withering Curse - A withering hex corrodes the target from within; they must succeed on a DC 17 Constitution save or be poisoned.","img":"icons/svg/poison.svg","weight":6,"range":[43,48],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"poisoned"}}},{"_id":"XmqhKk7jt9dLpiDh","type":0,"text":"Concussive Blast - A concussive shockwave hammers the target; they must succeed on a DC 17 Strength save or be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","weight":6,"range":[49,54],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"str","effectCondition":"prone"}}},{"_id":"OcXR6gtnHNxlNIhU","type":0,"text":"Arcane Annihilation - Magical fire engulfs the target. They take extra fire damage equal to three of the spell's damage dice at the start of each turn until Dispel Magic (DC 17) or similar.","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-yellow-orange.webp","weight":5,"range":[55,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3S","damageType":"fire"}}},{"_id":"JhuwZZ9l9Ks83IVr","type":0,"text":"Elemental Apocalypse - Your spell's element utterly overwhelms the target. Add extra damage equal to three of the spell's damage dice, of the spell's type.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3S","damageType":"spell"}}},{"_id":"50hBdGxrAA0hcoQY","type":0,"text":"Apocalyptic Blast - The force sends the target flying 60 feet, prone, stunned for 1 round, and takes extra force damage equal to three of the spell's damage dice.","img":"icons/svg/thrust.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3S","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"9yq2318OxkLS380L","type":0,"text":"Numbing Frost - Creeping frost locks the target's limbs; they must succeed on a DC 17 Strength save or be restrained.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"str","effectCondition":"restrained"}}},{"_id":"owVIoi4FRWtf84dB","type":0,"text":"Mind Spike - A lance of psychic force stabs the target's mind; they must succeed on a DC 17 Wisdom save or be frightened of you.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":5,"range":[75,79],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"wis","effectCondition":"frightened"}}},{"_id":"vvGJqmh32eApZCRW","type":0,"text":"Overwhelming Arcane Power - Your devastating spell deals additional force damage equal to four of the spell's damage dice.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":4,"range":[80,83],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"4S","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"Bj09cSGxIL61kL0d","type":0,"text":"Terrifying Magic - Your devastating spell terrifies the target to their core. They are frightened of you for 3 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":4,"range":[84,87],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"frightened","duration":3}}},{"_id":"qb6RjQnh36pykkQM","type":0,"text":"Arcane Vulnerability - Your magic leaves the target utterly exposed. Attacks against them have advantage for 3 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":4,"range":[88,91],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Arcane Vulnerability","duration":3}}},{"_id":"qV8EnseJlxsxbLCx","type":0,"text":"Soulscored - The spell scars the target's very soul, inflicting one level of exhaustion.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":3,"range":[92,94],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"exhaustion","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"Q3Nu55BEzGkktgy6","type":0,"text":"Soul Rending - If target has 50 HP or fewer, they must make a DC 17 Wisdom save or take 6d10 force extra damage.","img":"icons/svg/skull.svg","weight":3,"range":[95,97],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"wis","damageFormula":"6d10","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"yUPNcxhgOWzGKKKT","type":0,"text":"Arcane Lock - Binding sigils seize the target's body; they must succeed on a DC 17 Constitution save or be paralyzed.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":2,"range":[98,99],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"paralyzed"}}},{"_id":"1nUqNRVoVnGobmWM","type":0,"text":"Elemental Detonation - The spell's energy detonates catastrophically, dealing bonus damage equal to the spell's slot-scaled magnitude.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1SB","damageType":"spell"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":4,"attackType":"spell","resultType":"crit"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783951849387,"modifiedTime":1783951849387,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"GTIIzwbiXXrmi9Dw","name":"Tier 4 Spell Fumbles (Levels 13-20)","description":"Fumble effects for spell attacks at Tier 4 (Levels 13-20). Effects are legendary for master adventurers.","img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-fireball-smoke-strong-orange.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"mk6GE5p70a7qKz46","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your spell fizzles harmlessly with no additional penalty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","weight":6,"range":[1,6],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"U4n5EVuLtJTTMQEU","type":0,"text":"Grounded Magic - Your spell earths itself through your body. You have disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[7,14],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Grounded Magic","duration":1}}},{"_id":"qGJumYmKJp3yBART","type":0,"text":"Spell Recoil - The spell lashes back as it leaves you. You have disadvantage on your next ranged spell attack.","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","weight":8,"range":[15,22],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.rsak","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Spell Recoil","duration":0}}},{"_id":"ZFMAidGqLds1p78g","type":0,"text":"Arcane Hiccup - Your magic stutters and misfires. You have disadvantage on spell attacks until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":7,"range":[23,29],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":["attack.msak","attack.rsak"],"advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Arcane Hiccup","duration":1}}},{"_id":"k4mYNZGNROjyJzW1","type":0,"text":"Somatic Cramp - Your casting hand cramps violently. You have disadvantage on concentration checks until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":7,"range":[30,36],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"concentration","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Somatic Cramp","duration":1}}},{"_id":"aY2tllke8B2MUqC4","type":0,"text":"Arcane Backlash - Raw magic rebounds into you. Take force damage equal to one of the spell's damage dice.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":6,"range":[37,42],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1S","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"6ZiF7rs4ARDjRObp","type":0,"text":"Component Combustion - Your material components ignite in your grip. Take 1d6 fire damage.","img":"icons/svg/fire.svg","weight":6,"range":[43,48],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d6","damageType":"fire"}}},{"_id":"7zGru3gvmJHCBjRA","type":0,"text":"Telegraphed Magic - Your fumbled casting tips your hand. Enemies have advantage on their next saving throw against your spells.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":6,"range":[49,54],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Telegraphed Magic","duration":0}}},{"_id":"YmjVHlobvXvmhsb1","type":0,"text":"Exposed Weave - Your botched weave leaves you unguarded. Attacks against you have advantage until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[55,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Exposed Weave","duration":1}}},{"_id":"yTuJYq3qtRtnAEWH","type":0,"text":"Warped Focus - The recoil throws off your aim. You take a -2 penalty to attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"KanWHWhm6I3sRswl","type":0,"text":"Shattered Wards - The backlash shreds your protective wards. You take a -2 penalty to AC until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"75ymgM0S2g4U3IRw","type":0,"text":"Backlash Sprawl - The detonation throws you off your feet. You are knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/combat.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"QyWRZPlUi6SB8kX9","type":0,"text":"Magical Backlash - The spell's energy rebounds painfully. Take 1d8 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","weight":5,"range":[75,79],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d8","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"66tp2GnJRHQ9JMt6","type":0,"text":"Blinding Feedback - A blinding flash of misfired magic sears your eyes. You are blinded until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":4,"range":[80,83],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"u1jyemBHgt0ddyBo","type":0,"text":"Searing Recoil - Searing magical energy tears back into you. Take 1d10 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","weight":4,"range":[84,87],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d10","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"H4qONpe7XAiD55lW","type":0,"text":"Catastrophic Rebound - Your spell collapses inward. Make a DC 17 Constitution saving throw or take 5d6 force damage and be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":4,"range":[88,91],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","damageFormula":"5d6","damageType":"force","effectCondition":"prone","failEffect":"Take force damage and be knocked prone"}}},{"_id":"56cOQrvRE960BcUF","type":0,"text":"Feedback Stun - Arcane feedback locks every muscle rigid. You are stunned until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":3,"range":[92,94],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"stunned","duration":0}}},{"_id":"qd7vEf5iXYq1qOby","type":0,"text":"Mana Drain - The failed casting rips the vigor from you. You gain one level of exhaustion.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":3,"range":[95,97],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"exhaustion","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"l0eG9tuFe6CDe5QG","type":0,"text":"Wild Surge Jolt - Wild magic detonates through your body. Take 2d6 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":2,"range":[98,99],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"9LX0HLgNCBcR27NT","type":0,"text":"Misfired Blast - Your spell veers wildly and misfires at the nearest ally. Make a spell attack against the nearest ally; on a hit, they take the spell's damage.","img":"icons/svg/combat.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"attackAlly"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":4,"attackType":"spell","resultType":"fumble"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783951849387,"modifiedTime":1783951849387,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}